1. Ja *potpisujem* ugovor sa kompanijom. (I am *signing* a contract with the company.)
2. Oni će *potpisati* peticiju protiv odluke vlade. (They will *sign* a petition against the government's decision.)
3. Da li si *potpisao* listu prisustva? (Did you *sign* the attendance sheet?)
4. Njihov predsednik je već *potpisao* sporazum. (Their president has already *signed* the agreement.)
5. Molim vas da *potpišete* ovaj dokument. (Please *sign* this document.)
6. Ne mogu da *potpišem* to pismo, nije u skladu sa mojim principima. (I cannot *sign* that letter, it goes against my principles.)
7. *Potpisivanje* ugovora će se obaviti u ponedeljak. (The *signing* of the contract will take place on Monday.)
8. Ovaj ugovor zahteva *potpis* obe strane. (This contract requires the *signature* of both parties.)
9. Kada sam *potpisao* ugovor, nisam bio svestan posledica. (When I *signed* the contract, I was not aware of the consequences.)
10. Nije bilo dovoljno vremena za *potpisivanje* sporazuma. (There was not enough time for *signing* the agreement.)